---
---

<div class="text-center">
  <span class="eyebrow">Pricing</span>
  <h2 class="mt-5 text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
    Free to learn. Pro to prove you can ship.
  </h2>
  <p class="mt-4 text-lg copy-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    Master the delivery loop with a full project — free, forever. Pro adds the team simulation, AI-enhanced reviews, and a delivery record that gets you hired.
  </p>

  <div class="pricing-grid mt-14 text-left">

    <!-- Free -->
    <div class="pricing-card surface-card flex flex-col">
      <div class="p-6 sm:p-7 flex-1 flex flex-col">
        <p class="tier-label copy-subtle">Free</p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1">
          <span class="price-amount text-white">$0</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-1 price-sub">Free forever</p>
        <p class="mt-3 feature-desc">Learn the full delivery loop — code, test, PR, merge.</p>

        <div class="mt-5 pt-5 border-t border-[var(--color-border-subtle)] flex-1">
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-green">✓</span>Browser IDE, terminal, git</li>
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-green">✓</span>1 project with 6 labs</li>
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-green">✓</span>Test-based quality gates</li>
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-green">✓</span>Basic delivery record</li>
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-green">✓</span>Self-paced, no credit card</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <a href="#notify" class="mt-7 pricing-btn pricing-btn-ghost">
          Start for free <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Founding Member -->
    <div class="pricing-card pricing-card-featured surface-card flex flex-col relative">
      <div class="pricing-badge">
        <span>Limited — 50 spots</span>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 sm:p-7 pt-8 sm:pt-9 flex-1 flex flex-col">
        <p class="tier-label text-[var(--color-accent)]">Founding Member</p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1">
          <span class="price-amount text-[var(--color-accent)]">$15</span>
          <span class="text-sm copy-subtle">/mo</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-1 price-sub">Locked — never increases</p>
        <p class="mt-3 feature-desc">Everything in Pro at half price. Shape the product.</p>

        <div class="mt-5 pt-5 border-t border-[var(--color-accent)]/10 flex-1">
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-cyan">✓</span><strong class="text-white">All Pro features included</strong></li>
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-cyan">✓</span>Direct founder access</li>
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-cyan">✓</span>Vote on upcoming labs</li>
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-cyan">✓</span>Founding badge on profile</li>
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-cyan">✓</span>Early access to everything</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <a href="#notify" class="mt-7 btn-primary cta-glow w-full text-center">
          Claim your spot <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <p class="mt-2 text-center text-[0.65rem] copy-subtle">Closes when 50 spots fill.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Pro -->
    <div class="pricing-card surface-card flex flex-col">
      <div class="p-6 sm:p-7 flex-1 flex flex-col">
        <p class="tier-label text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">Pro</p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1">
          <span class="price-amount text-white">$29</span>
          <span class="text-sm copy-subtle">/mo</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-1 price-sub">Or $19/mo billed annually</p>
        <p class="mt-3 feature-desc">Ship like a teammate. Prove it to hiring managers.</p>

        <div class="mt-5 pt-5 border-t border-[var(--color-border-subtle)] flex-1">
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-green">✓</span>Persona code reviews</li>
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-green">✓</span>AI-enhanced feedback</li>
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-green">✓</span>Chat, standups, sprint board</li>
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-green">✓</span>4 curated learning tracks</li>
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-green">✓</span>Private community + jobs</li>
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-green">✓</span>Founder coaching sessions</li>
            <li class="feature-item"><span class="check check-green">✓</span>Full delivery record</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <a href="#notify" class="mt-7 pricing-btn pricing-btn-green">
          Join early access <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <p class="mt-10 text-sm copy-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    Free gets you the skills. Pro gets you the proof. Less than a dollar a day. Cancel anytime.
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .pricing-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .pricing-grid {
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }
  }

  .tier-label {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .price-amount {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .price-sub {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .feature-desc {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .pricing-card {
    transition: border-color 300ms ease, box-shadow 300ms ease, opacity 300ms ease;
  }

  .pricing-card,
  .pricing-card:hover {
    transform: none !important;
  }

  .pricing-card-featured {
    overflow: visible;
    border-color: rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.3);
    box-shadow:
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04),
      0 0 0 1px rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.08),
      0 0 40px rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.05),
      0 16px 48px rgba(1, 8, 23, 0.55);
  }

  .pricing-card-featured,
  .pricing-card-featured:hover {
    border-color: rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.3);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .pricing-card:not(.pricing-card-featured),
    .pricing-card:not(.pricing-card-featured):hover {
      transform: scale(0.94) !important;
      opacity: 0.88;
    }

    .pricing-card:not(.pricing-card-featured):hover {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .pricing-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    z-index: 3;
  }

  .pricing-badge span {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.28rem 0.8rem;
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2dd4ff, #00f5b4);
    color: #031224;
    white-space: nowrap;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.25);
  }

  .feature-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.45rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .check {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .check-cyan { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .check-green { color: var(--color-accent-2); }

  .pricing-btn {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.65rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.55rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: white;
    transition: border-color 200ms ease, box-shadow 200ms ease;
  }

  .pricing-btn-ghost {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .pricing-btn-ghost:hover {
    border-color: rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.35);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .pricing-btn-green {
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 245, 180, 0.3);
  }

  .pricing-btn-green:hover {
    border-color: rgba(0, 245, 180, 0.5);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 245, 180, 0.06);
  }
</style>
